reviewText:
OK I don't own this so I shouldn't be giving a review but....
The cover is indicative of a Payless release from Australia. You get Payless from the $2-5 bargain bins at our equivalent of Wa***rt. They produce poor quality VHS rips (like Alpha) and the recent releases (2005 and onwards) are OK but certainly not the asking price of $28. Avoid.....
